Any tips on 55+ only areas?  Did Gantru's tonight in UP, and they have about a 52-58 range.  Small 4 man group got about a 2 blues in an hour (AAxp at 60).  It pisses me off really.  A 52 Gantru gives me less than half of what a 58 Gantru gets me, but both are about as hard.  Verant should really go update the levels on things now that 50+ isn't arbitrary.<br>
