<br>
Only the 55+ mobs are giving the big exp bonus. Everything under 55 is the same as it always was.<br>
<br>
This seems a little stupid to me considering the dificulty of most of those mobs in the 50-55 range. I'd like to see Verant add another bonus in to even out 50-55 so that they are worth the extra effort it takes to kill them.<br>
<br>
Let me give you an example.<br>
<br>
Akheva.<br>
<br>
60Cleric, 60Bard, 60Warrior, 58Warrior, 60Monk(me), 60Enchanter with L46 Shrouded Anisher (SK) as a pet (love dire charm), all decked in mostly NToV or equivalent gear, all epiced.<br>
<br>
We start clearing our way in. <br>
<br>
5 regular Centi kills (L45-L49) yield about 1% AAxp (all are on AA except the 58Warrior).<br>
<br>
We go after Mindworms (the big ones in the southeast corner) to see how the new xp changes worked out. Mindworms attack very fast, hit harder than the Centi, and are L52-L55, and will summon your ass. They also instantly drain your caster's mana pools if they get on them. I'd say that's a substantially higher risk vs reward.<br>
<br>
I botched the pull a bit (tricky split) and we end up with 3 at once. No prob, one war on each and me on the third. Cleric was on the ball, we killed all three of them, was a tense fight and it was a load of fun as none of us were expecting that. I swear it looked like just 2 of them coming down the hall. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Not even 1% AAxp. Pulled two more Mindworms, finally got 1% AAxp out of them. Looks like it takes 4-5 Mindworms to equal out to 5 Centi. That is total bullshit.<br>
<br>
So, we decided to scrap mindworms. We went up and farmed Vadyn's guards for a bit to check out the changes further. Vadyn's guards (Rubble Rousers) are L58, have a shitload of HP, hit a ton harder than the mindworms, summon and enrage. Those L58 guards gave us 1% AA per kill. We farmed them for awhile (fast repop) then got bored and went back to killing Centi.<br>
<br>
With that group we can take 5 centi at a time and kill them in under a minute. We just did what we always do... mass centi genocide. That provided us with far more xp than wurms or Rubble Rousers. We could kill 15 centi in the time it took for one rouser and or for 3 wurms.<br>
<br>
15 centi (45-49) = 3%aa in 4 minutes - no risk, no downtime<br>
1 rubble ( 58 ) = 1%aa in 4 minutes - some risk, no downtime<br>
3 wurms (52-55) = 1.5%aa in 4 minutes - lots of risk, some downtime<br>
<br>
So, tell me again why I should bother with the tougher mobs?<br>
<br>
Verant needs to rework it like this...<br>
<br>
15 centi (45-49) = 3%aa in 4 minutes - no risk, no downtime<br>
1 rubble ( 58 ) = 2%aa in 4 minutes - some risk, no downtime<br>
3 wurms (52-55) = 4%aa in 4 minutes - lots of risk, some downtime<br>
<br>
Stick a bonus on mobs that are 50-55, and I'd up the bonus on 56-66 a bit as well. The carrot just isn't big enough. <p><b>Raviel Darkfyre</b><BR>
